('vi', 9, 'V chng ti', NULL, '<div class=\"raw-html-embed\"><div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\n        <div class=\"single-excerpt\">\n            <p class=\"font-large\">Ngi ta n trnh nhc n Cha Kito khi ni n mc lch s bng cch ni Trc cng nguyn v sau cng nguyn. Nhng nguyn ting anh: Before Chirst, After Chirst  trc Cha Kito, sau Cha Kito  ngi ta s lch s ca Kito gio.  l li chia s ca cha c trch Gioan trong Thnh l thng k Cng on sinh vin Cng gio y dc vo lc 19h15, ngy 11.05.2017 ti n thnh Gierado, Gio x Thi H.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"entry-main-content\">\n            <h2>Cuc sng l nhng php mu</h2>\n            <hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n                <figure class=\"alignleft is-resized\">\n                    <img class=\"border-radius-5\" src=\"/themes/ultra/images/thumbnail-14.jpg\">\n                </figure>\n            </div>\n            <p>Khi u bi ging ca mnh cha ni n mt trong nhng kh khn ln nht Gio Hi ni chung v ngi tn hu ni ring  chnh l nim tin vo Thin Cha. Chnh khng hong nim tin gy nn chin tranh, gy nn th hn v cht chc. Lng tin khng ch nh hng ln c nhn m thi nhng ln ton th gii. Hm nay, Cha cho chng ta thy lng tin l khi u, l mu cht  con ngi ng vng gia trm chiu th thch.</p>\n            <h5> ngha l g?</h5>\n            <p>Hai bi c hm nay u i t lch s, Cha Giesu tin bo k s np thy. Ngi chn Giuda khng phi chn nhm, nhng Ngi ni r trong bi Tin Mng rng li kinh thnh phi c ng nghim: K gi tay chm chung mt a vi con li gi gt p con. Trong bi c mt, Phaolo ni v avit  ng nghim li Kinh thnh  ni,  anh ch em Do thi nhn ra c li tin bo qua lch s l cha Giesu.</p>\n            <hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-dots\">\n            <p> c c lng tin ni con ngi, Cha Giesu  khai mo trong mt chng trnh lch s di tp. Lch s Cu c loan bo ng vi nhng g  xy ra vi Cha Giesu Kito. Mt trit gia ngi Php ni rng: Kito gio c mt nn tng c tin vng chc  l lch s, nhng Kito gio qun i im quan trng ny v ngy nay i nng v pha thn hc.</p>\n            <h2>Kt lun</h2>\n            <hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\">\n            <p>Cha nhc li: Kito Gio cm r su, tri di v c ng nghim trong lch s thnh kinh ngang qua nhng con ngi, ni chn, a im c th. Nhn li lch s, cc ngy l x hi, ngy ngh u lin quan n Kito gio v xut pht t Kito gio.</p>\n\n\n            <h2>Tng lai</h2>\n            <hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\">\n            <p>Cha ni n bin c c M hin ra ti Fatima 100 nm l mt bin c lch s c thi gian, khng gian, nhn vt v s ip c th khng phi con ngi t dng nn hay hoang tng.</p>\n            <p>Nim tin ca mi chng ta phi da vo lch s ch khng phi m h. Khi nhn li qu kh ta bit rng lng tin   c Thin Cha khai mo t rt sm. Cc thnh Tng   ng trn bnh din lch s  minh chng nim tin ca con ngi vo Giave Thin Cha.</p>\n            <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3\">\n                <ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\">\n                    <li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n                        <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"border-radius-5\" src=\"/themes/ultra/images/thumbnail-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n                        <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"border-radius-5\" src=\"/themes/ultra/images/thumbnail-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n                        <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"border-radius-5\" src=\"/themes/ultra/images/thumbnail-10.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n            </figure>\n            <p>Nhiu ngi thi nay bit lch s nhng khng bit Cha Kito l ai v h n trnh Cha Giesu. Cha Giesu i vo lch s  t cho con ngi cng ch ca s sng l g v Thin Cha l ai cng nhng li tin bo  cng c lng tin cho con ngi.</p>\n            <hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-dots\">\n           <blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\">\n                <p>S tin b ca cng ngh da trn vic lm cho n ph hp  bn thm ch khng thc s nhn thy n, v vy n l mt phn ca cuc sng hng ngy.</p><cite>B. Johnso</cite>\n            </blockquote>\n            <p class=\"text-center\">\n                <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"d-inline\" src=\"assets/imgs/ads-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>'),
('vi', 10, 'Cookie Policy', NULL, '<h3>EU Cookie Consent</h3><p> s dng trang web ny, chng ti ang s dng Cookie v thu thp mt s D liu.  tun th GDPR ca Lin minh Chu u, chng ti cho bn la chn nu bn cho php chng ti s dng mt s Cookie nht nh v thu thp mt s D liu.</p><h4>D liu cn thit</h4><p>D liu cn thit l cn thit  chy Trang web bn ang truy cp v mt k thut. Bn khng th hy kch hot chng.</p><p>- Session Cookie: PHP s dng Cookie  xc nh phin ca ngi dng. Nu khng c Cookie ny, trang web s khng hot ng.</p><p>- XSRF-Token Cookie: Laravel t ng to \"token\" CSRF cho mi phin ngi dng ang hot ng do ng dng qun l. Token ny c s dng  xc minh rng ngi dng  xc thc l ngi thc s a ra yu cu i vi ng dng.</p>');

